Package: BiocWorkflowsCanary
Title: Canary Package for bioconductor/workflows CI Validation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Levi", "Waldron", email = "lwaldron.research@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A minimal R package used as a canary to validate that the
    bioconductor/workflows reusable GitHub Actions workflows execute correctly
    end-to-end against the current Bioconductor devel container.
    This package has no real functionality; its sole purpose is to serve as
    the check target for the scheduled canary CI workflow.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
biocViews: Infrastructure
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
